name: Experiment Or Die #111
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. 1982 was a little early to have a crush on anyone considering I would have been 1 year old at that point, but none the less the ladies of the original Blade Runner were pretty great even for a dystopian future. If your life span were only 5 years long what would you do? Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
